        <h2>2025's Biggest Celebrity Lash Trends</h2>

        <h3>1. The "Wet Look" Lash</h3>
        <p>Popularized by celebrities like Megan Fox and Hailey Bieber:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Glossy, clumped appearance</li>
          <li>Darker base with wispy tips</li>
          <li>Strategically spaced spikes</li>
          <li>Natural yet editorial aesthetic</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Perfect for beach photos and summer events</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. Fluffy Manga Lashes</h3>
        <p>Made famous by Ariana Grande and Rosalía:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Extreme volume and separation</li>
          <li>Open, doll-like effect</li>
          <li>Mixed lengths for dimension</li>
          <li>Dramatic but surprisingly wearable</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Ideal for photo shoots and special occasions</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. The Minimalist Natural</h3>
        <p>Embraced by Zendaya and Emma Watson:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your-lashes-but-better philosophy</li>
          <li>Subtle length and curl enhancement</li>
          <li>No obvious extensions</li>
          <li>Effortlessly chic</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Perfect for everyday Orange County lifestyle</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4. Fox Eye Lashes</h3>
        <p>Spotted on Bella Hadid and Kendall Jenner:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Elongated outer corner emphasis</li>
          <li>Creates lifted, cat-eye effect</li>
          <li>Strategic length mapping</li>
          <li>Sultry and sophisticated</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Great for evenings at South Coast Plaza or date nights</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5. Colored Lash Accents</h3>
        <p>Pioneered by Billie Eilish and Dua Lipa:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Subtle colored tips or accents</li>
          <li>Brown lashes for warmth</li>
          <li>Blue or purple undertones</li>
          <li>Festival-ready fun</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Perfect for Coachella season and music festivals</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>6. The Wispy Hybrid</h3>
        <p>Taylor Swift and Selena Gomez's go-to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Mix of classic and volume techniques</li>
          <li>Feathered, textured appearance</li>
          <li>Natural movement and dimension</li>
          <li>Universally flattering</li>
          <li><strong>OC Adaptation:</strong> Ideal for professional and social settings</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Celebrity Lash Styles by Face Shape</h2>

        <h3>Round Face (Selena Gomez, Chrissy Teigen)</h3>
        <p>Best styles to elongate:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cat-eye mapping with longer outer corners</li>
          <li>Upward curl to create lift</li>
          <li>Medium volume to avoid widening effect</li>
          <li>Angular, elongated shapes</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Oval Face (Beyoncé, Rihanna)</h3>
        <p>Lucky you - almost everything works!</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Can handle dramatic volume</li>
          <li>Experimental styles look great</li>
          <li>Both natural and bold work beautifully</li>
          <li>Perfect canvas for trending styles</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Heart-Shaped Face (Zendaya, Reese Witherspoon)</h3>
        <p>Balance wider forehead with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Doll-eye mapping (longer in center)</li>
          <li>Fuller volume in the middle</li>
          <li>Softer, rounded shapes</li>
          <li>Avoid extreme cat-eyes</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Square Face (Angelina Jolie, Olivia Wilde)</h3>
        <p>Soften angular features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Rounded, wispy styles</li>
          <li>Soft curls (C or D)</li>
          <li>Natural, feathered looks</li>
          <li>Avoid harsh, dramatic lines</li>
        </ul>

