        <h3>The Zendaya Effect</h3>
        <p>Her natural-yet-perfect lashes at the Met Gala sparked a movement toward "invisible" lash extensions that enhance without looking obvious.</p>

        <h3>Megan Fox's Wet Lash Revolution</h3>
        <p>Her glossy, intentionally clumped lashes broke traditional rules and started a major trend in editorial lash styling.</p>

        <h3>Ariana Grande's Manga Influence</h3>
        <p>Her anime-inspired fluffy lashes brought extreme volume back into fashion after years of natural trends.</p>

        <h3>Hailey Bieber's Everyday Glam</h3>
        <p>She proved that you can wear beautiful lashes for yoga, coffee runs, and casual outings - not just special events.</p>

